What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A great opportunity to improve as a singer.

Performance is a low-stress lessons-for-credit course. I would definitely recommend the course to every student. The course allows one to improve in one's instrument/voice and to get credit while enjoying it.

I would recommend voice lessons to another student, especially if they are looking for free lessons or a quick fifth class, but I felt a bit like I was taking them needlessly and should have been taking another class instead.
